item.title: Can anyone give me coordinates to pest control?
item.dc:creator: @sonjichan sonjichan
item.description:
@sonjichan wrote:

Pest control normally would exist south of ape atoll, however it does not exist in any conceivable serverbase other than jagex. The new client cache has it, but there’s no server base written for it yet, at least that I know about or have access to. if you want however I’ll give you a list of coordinates that I spent like night discovering, was fixing doors and teleports, and needed to find the underground areas. for instance all of the runecraft temples are in a straight line from west to east, with the exception of the death temple which curves off to the south. Here’s the coords. Personally I have no idea what the skyscraper thing is, and I could’ve swore that jagex got rid of the blackhole… guess not.

//Coords to repair/add entrance to - Sonjichan

2978,9871 = blackhole
2038,4531 = mod meeting room.
2242,3278 = Tirawyn
2719,9431 = Dragon Lairs
3232,2902 = Pyramid
2462,4775 = Frog Token Island
2099,4440 = Prison Pete minigame
2006,4437 = Christmas Toyshop
1890,4517 = Mysterious skyscraper.
1867,4621 = Death Temple
2127,3930 = Weird dark wildly area (perhaps cheezscape only)
2375,4393 = Zanaris
2460,4382 = Strange mining area
2589,4499 = Gnome glider hanger.
2664,4707 = Miscellania
2795,4585 = Odd mining caverns
2717,4838 = Water runecrafting temple (run east or west with ::noclip for more)
2604,4774 = wood forrest random
2269,4758 = Troll Cave room
2917,4452 = Mysterious island of glowy water

Coords individually found by sonjichan
